parameters.name: OrderId
parameters.description: The ID of the ticket for the data change.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description:
The number of the page to return.

Valid values: an integer that is greater than 0.

Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page.

parameters.name: Tid
parameters.description: The ID of the tenant. You can call the [GetUserActiveTenant](~~198073~~) or [ListUserTenants](~~198074~~) operation to query the ID of the tenant.
